          <span class="btn-content">
<svg aria-hidden="true" class="icon icon-lg btn-icon mr-xs" role="presentation" data-icon="search" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9.256 14.756a5.5 5.5 0 1 0 0-11 5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0 11Z"/><path d="M19.856 19.856c-.5.5-1.2.5-1.7.1l-2.8-2.8c-.5-.5-.5-1.2 0-1.7l.1-.1c.5-.5 1.2-.5 1.7 0l2.8 2.8c.4.5.4 1.2-.1 1.7Z" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><path d="m13.125 13.25 2.219 2.156" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>            Hae
